hostel_alt_img: a large room with a large table and chairs at Motel One Paris-Porte Dorée in Paris
description: The air-conditioned rooms feature a desk and a flat-screen TV. They also have a private bathroom with a shower, a hairdryer and free toiletries. All rooms are serviced by a lift and free WiFi is available throughout the property.

hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with a view of the ocean at Citadines Les Halles Paris in Paris
description: The apartments at Citadines Les Halles Paris are equipped with a telephone and flat-screen TV. Each apartment has a private bathroom with bathtub and an equipped kitchen with a microwave, dishwasher and fridge.

hostel_name: Holiday Inn Express Paris-Canal De La Villette, an IHG Hotel
hostel_alt_img: a city street at night with lights on at Holiday Inn Express Paris-Canal De La Villette, an IHG Hotel in Paris
description: The Canal de la Villette Holiday Inn offers soundproofed rooms equipped with air conditioning and a TV with 100 TV channels. They each have a private bathroom, and are serviced by a lift. Free high-speed WiFi is provided in all areas.

hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with a bed and a television at Novotel Suites Paris Montreuil Vincennes in Paris
description: Satellite TV and unlimited calls within France are standard facilities in the suites at Novotel Suites Paris Montreuil Vincennes. All suites are air-conditioned and also feature a microwave and a refrigerator.
Hotel d'Amiens is located in Paris between Gare du Nord and Gare de l’Est Train Stations. It offers rooms with a bath or a shower, satellite TV and free WiFi.

hostel_alt_img: a living room filled with furniture and a table at Citadines Bastille Marais Paris in Paris
description: The residence offers self-catering accommodations with free internet access. They all have a bathroom, an equipped kitchen and a seating area.

hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with a large bed and a large window at Citadines République Paris in Paris
description: Just a 2-minute walk from Parmentier Metro Station, this 3-star residence offers a 24-hour reception with luggage storage. You can walk to Place de la République and Père Lachaise Cemetery in 10 minutes.

hostel_alt_img: a living room filled with furniture and a fireplace at Résidence & Spa Le Prince Régent in Paris
description: Résidence & Spa Le Prince Régent is located 2 minutes from the Sorbonne University in Paris’s Latin Quarter. It features spacious apartments and a luxury spa centre, which guests have access to for an extra charge.

hostel_name: Aparthotel Adagio Paris Centre Tour Eiffel
hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with a bed and a desk at Aparthotel Adagio Paris Centre Tour Eiffel in Paris
description: All studios and apartments at this aparthotel come with a fully equipped kitchen with a stove, microwave, fridge and dishwasher. The apartment features a dining area and a seating area with adjustable furniture and an LCD TV. The aparthotel is serviced by a lift.

hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with a bed, chair, and window at Hotel Elysees Opera in Paris
description: Located in the chic 8th district in Paris, this hotel offers modern guest rooms with a balcony. It has a 24-hour reception with a tour desk and ticket service.

hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with two beds and two lamps at Hotel de L'Esperance in Paris
description: Located a 2-minute walk from the lively rue Mouffetard in Paris, Hotel de L'Esperance offers an inner courtyard. Place Monge and the Latin district are a 10-minute's walk away. Free WiFi is featured throughout the property.

hostel_alt_img: a city street filled with lots of tall buildings at Novotel Paris Centre Tour Eiffel in Paris
description: The spacious rooms have en suite facilities and are contemporary in style. Free WiFi access is provided throughout.

hostel_alt_img: a building with a clock on the front of it at Hôtel Aiglon in Paris
description: Located in the heart of the Montparnasse district, this design hotel is just 30 m from the Raspail Metro stop. Guest rooms are modern and stylish with free Wi-Fi access.

hostel_alt_img: a table with a glass of wine and a plate of food at Pullman Paris Tour Eiffel in Paris
description: Decorated in a contemporary style, the bright guest rooms offer panoramic views of Paris. They includes a flat-screen TV with free access to the latest films, an iPod dock and free WiFi access. Most of the rooms have a balcony, while some also have a stunning view of the Eiffel Tower or the garden.

hostel_alt_img: a man in a hat is on a counter at Grand Hôtel Amelot in Paris
description: Located in the 11th district of Paris, a 5-minute walk from the Marais district and Place des Vosges Park, Grand Hôtel Amelot offers a 24-hour reception, concierge service and luggage storage.

hostel_alt_img: a living room filled with furniture and a large window at B&B HOTEL Paris 17 Batignolles in Paris
description: Each room is equipped with an LCD TV with satellite channels, a desk, a safety box and tea and coffee making facilities. The private bathrooms feature a bathtub and a hairdryer.

hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with a bed and a television at Austin's Saint Lazare Hotel in Paris
description: This Austin's hotel is located in central Paris, next to Saint-Lazare Train Station and 800 m from Opéra Garnier. It offers soundproofed guest rooms with air-conditioning, flat-screen satellite TV and free WiFi.

hostel_name: MEININGER Hotel Paris Porte de Vincennes
hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with tables, chairs, and umbrellas at MEININGER Hotel Paris Porte de Vincennes in Paris
description: Guest rooms at the hotel are equipped with a seating area, a flat-screen TV with cable channels and a private bathroom with a hairdryer and a shower. At MEININGER Hotel Paris Porte de Vincennes each room includes bed linen and towels.

hostel_alt_img: a large building with a large clock on the front of it at Hotel Lutetia in Paris
description: A Paris landmark, the hotel features 184 rooms including 40 suites and 7 signature suites. Each of them features complimentary WiFi, media hubs and marble bathrooms . Some rooms have a balcony with views of the Eiffel Tower, and some suites feature a rooftop terrace with a 360° view of Paris.

hostel_alt_img: a bedroom with a bed and a desk at Hôtel Korner Etoile in Paris
description: Guest rooms at Hôtel Korner Etoile are simply furnished and have parquet floors. Each has a flat-screen TV with cable channels and an en suite bathroom with a shower.

hostel_alt_img: A bed or beds in a room at Hôtel Rosalie
description: Located in the Gobelins district, recent renovated in 2022 design hotel features a duplex terrace and private shaded rooftop terrace for their guests enjoyment. A portion of their rooms highlights view of the Eiffel Tower and Parisienne city landscapes.

hostel_alt_img: a bedroom with a bed, bookshelves and a lamp at HotelHome Paris 16 in Paris
description: HotelHome Paris 16 is located in Paris’s 16th arrondissement, 1.5 km from The Bois de Boulogne. It offers air-conditioned, self-catering apartments with free Wi-Fi internet access.

hostel_alt_img: a living room filled with furniture and a window at Studios dans l'Hypercentre in Bordeaux
description: Located in Bordeaux, near Museum of Aquitaine, Great Bell Bordeaux and Saint-Michel Basilica, Studios dans l'Hypercentre features free WiFi.

hostel_alt_img: a large room with a large clock on the wall at Le Boutique Hotel & Spa in Bordeaux
description: Located at the heart of Bordeaux’s historic centre, Le Boutique Hotel is an 18th-century town house surrounding a lush, green courtyard. It offers a 140 m² terrace shaded by a 100-year-old chestnut tree.

hostel_alt_img: a living room filled with furniture and a large window at Austin's Arts Et Metiers Hotel in Paris
description: This Austin's Hotel is located in the Marais district of central Paris, 500 m from Place de la Republique and 600 m from the Pompidou Centre. The hotel has a 24-hour reception which provides computers with free internet access for all guests.

hostel_alt_img: a kitchen with a table, chairs and a refrigerator at Appart’City Confort Bordeaux Chartrons in Bordeaux
description: Studios and apartments feature air conditioning, a working area and a flat-screen TV. There is a seating and/or dining area in some units. There is also a kitchenette, fitted with a microwave.

hostel_alt_img: an empty room with a blue wall and blue chairs at Hôtel Gérando in Paris
description: Hotel Gérando is located in the Montmartre area in Paris. The hotel features a 24-hour reception, a luggage storage and free WiFi.

hostel_name: Montempô Bordeaux Centre - Bassins à flot
hostel_alt_img: a living room filled with furniture and a table at Montempô Bordeaux Centre - Bassins à flot in Bordeaux
description: The accommodation comes with a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with shower and free toiletries, while the kitchenette has a microwave, a fridge and a stovetop.

hostel_alt_img: a large building with a clock on the side of it at Ténéo Apparthotel Bordeaux Maritime in Bordeaux
description: The accommodation features a flat-screen TV. There is a seating and/or dining area in some units. There is also a kitchenette, equipped with a microwave. A refrigerator and kettle are also offered. Towels are provided.

hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with a bed, chair, and nightstand at Residhome Bordeaux in Bordeaux
description: All rooms are equipped with a flat-screen TV. Certain units have a seating area for your convenience. Each room is fitted with a private bathroom fitted with a shower. Extras include free toiletries and a hairdryer.

hostel_alt_img: a large body of water with a large building at Radisson Blu Hotel Bordeaux in Bordeaux
description: Set in Bordeaux, within 700 m of La Cite du Vin and Chaban Delmas Bridge, Radisson Blu Hotel Bordeaux features accommodation with a terrace and free WiFi. Featuring a bar, this 4-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with a private bathroom. The hotel provides a French restaurant.

hostel_name: Appart-Hôtel Mer & Golf City Bordeaux Bassins à flot
hostel_alt_img: a bedroom with a large bed and a large window at Appart-Hôtel Mer & Golf City Bordeaux Bassins à flot in Bordeaux
description: The pet-friendly accommodation is air conditioned and is fitted with a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. All units feature a dining area and some of them have a large terrace. There is also a kitchenette, equipped with a dishwasher, a microwave and a toaster. A refrigerator is also provided, as well as a coffee machine and a kettle. Each room overlooks a pedestrian area.

hostel_alt_img: a building with a sign on the side of it at Quality Hotel Bordeaux Centre in Bordeaux
description: Each air-conditioned room is fully equipped with a flat-screen TV, a wireless TV casting device and a Nespresso coffee machine. All rooms are serviced by a lift.

hostel_alt_img: a table that has a bunch of flowers in it at Campanile Bordeaux Centre - Gare Saint-Jean in Bordeaux
description: Guest rooms all have a desk, a courtesy tray, a telephone and individually-controlled air conditioning and heating. Each room features a bathroom with a large walk-in shower, a hairdryer and toiletries.

hostel_alt_img: a bedroom with a bed, chair, table and window at Residhotel Galerie Tatry in Bordeaux
description: The apartments at Galerie Tatry are air-conditioned, depending on the season, and have a modern décor. They each feature a kitchenette with a microwave and fridge and a seating area with satellite TV. Bedroom and bathroom linens are provided.

hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with a view of the ocean at Renaissance Bordeaux Hotel in Bordeaux
description: Renaissance Bordeaux Hotel features a restaurant, fitness centre, a bar and shared lounge in Bordeaux.  Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk and room service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The hotel has an indoor pool and a concierge service.

hostel_alt_img: a bedroom with a bed and a lamp at Victoria Garden Bordeaux Centre in Bordeaux
description: An LCD TV and Wi-Fi access are provided in each apartment at Victoria Garden Bordeaux Centre. The bathroom includes a hairdryer and the kitchenette has a microwave and fridge.

hostel_alt_img: a bedroom with a bed and a window at Appart'City Bordeaux Centre in Bordeaux
description: The spacious apartments feature free internet access. Each apartment has a dining area and a kitchenette equipped with a microwave and a fridge. All apartments are serviced by a lift.

hostel_name: Novotel Bordeaux Centre Gare Saint Jean
hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with a bed, chair, desk and a television at Novotel Bordeaux Centre Gare Saint Jean in Bordeaux
description: All the spacious Novotel Bordeaux rooms offer a desk, a courtesy tray and a telephone, as well as individually set air conditioning. They also come with a private bathroom fitted with a bath tub or a shower, a hairdryer and separate toilet.

hostel_alt_img: a wine glass sitting on top of a counter top at Campanile Bordeaux Nord - Le Lac in Bordeaux
description: All of the rooms have tea and coffee making facilities and cable TV.

hostel_alt_img: a kitchen with a microwave and a sink at City Résidence Bordeaux Centre in Bordeaux
description: It offers modern apartments and studios with free WiFi. All the apartments have air conditioning. Each one has a flat-screen TV, a desk and bathroom with hairdryer. The kitchenette is equipped with a microwave, stove and refrigerator. Bed linen and towels are included.

hostel_alt_img: a woman standing in front of a counter filled with luggage at Moxy Bordeaux in Bordeaux
description: Moxy Bordeaux has a restaurant, bar, a shared lounge and garden in Bordeaux. Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk and a concierge service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The hotel features family rooms.

hostel_alt_img: a large kitchen with a lot of furniture at Staycity Aparthotels Bordeaux City Centre in Bordeaux
description: Accommodation is fitted with air conditioning, a fully equipped kitchenette, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with shower, a hairdryer and free toiletries. A microwave, a fridge and stovetop are also provided, as well as a kettle and a coffee machine.

hostel_alt_img: a hotel room with a bed, chair, and table at Hilton Garden Inn Bordeaux Centre in Bordeaux
description: At the hotel, all rooms come with a wardrobe. At Hilton Garden Inn Bordeaux Centre the rooms are equipped with a desk, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom.

hostel_alt_img: a large room with tables and chairs in it at Aparthotel Adagio Bordeaux Centre Gambetta in Bordeaux
description: Each apartment is equipped with satellite TV and a kitchen with table and chairs.  The one-bedroom apartments offer a separate living room.

hostel_name: Ténéo Apparthotel Bordeaux Gare Saint Jean
hostel_alt_img: a room with a bed, chair, desk and a television at Ténéo Apparthotel Bordeaux Gare Saint Jean in Bordeaux
description: The apartments and studios at Ténéo Suites include a kitchenette, telephone and flat-screen TV. The apartments are accessible by lift.

hostel_alt_img: a restaurant with tables and chairs in it at Eklo Bordeaux Centre Bastide in Bordeaux
description: At the hotel rooms have a desk and a private bathroom.

hostel_alt_img: a living room filled with furniture and decor at Hôtel Life Bordeaux Gare - BG in Bordeaux
description: Located in Bordeaux and with Saint-Michel Basilica reachable within less than 1 km, Hôtel Life Bordeaux Gare - BG features express check-in and check-out, non-smoking rooms, a bar, free WiFi throughout the property and a shared lounge. The property is around 2.6 km from Saint-André Cathedral, 1.8 km from Place de la Bourse and 3 km from Grand Théâtre de Bordeaux. The accommodation provides a fitness centre, evening entertainment and a 24-hour front desk.

hostel_alt_img: a bed room with a sign on the wall at MEININGER Hotel Bordeaux Gare Saint-Jean in Bordeaux
description: At the hotel, rooms include a desk, a flat-screen TV, a private bathroom, bed linen and towels.
